imdb.title: Thieves Row
plot: _Thieves Row_ (qv) follows a squad of professional bank robbers as they struggle to survive the trappings of corruption in their own community and the Los Angeles Police Department.

Shark, Cobra, Tiger and Lewis have become professionals at what they do.... robbing banks. Each one of them bring an expertise and as a team they have robberies down to a science. Shark and Cobra are the negotiators who hold up the banks. Tiger is the muscle, a support man when shit hits the fan and Lewis is the driver.
